      "role": "user",
      "content": "the house is so quiet today. i keep walking into the kitchen thinking he's just in the other room, but then i remember. it's like i'm just a ghost walking through these rooms. everything feels so empty and pointless. i dont even know why i bother getting out of bed anymore.",
