      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is not weird; it is a sign that your mind is trying to protect you from the unbearable reality of the pain. The darkness where you sit is not empty; it is the only place where you can finally breathe without the crushing weight of your own thoughts. You do not need to fix anything right now, because the only thing that matters is that you are still here, even if you are broken.",
